                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Wireless is generally fine for online gameplay though transferring files between the two computers it will seem very slow (also playing in-house games between the two computers will be slower than wired 100Mbps). Personally though I prefer wired networking to wireless as there are things that can interfere with wireless and it's more prone to hacking attempts (if your neighbors or a random person wandering by feels like trying). If running cable isn't a problem then buy something like a Linksys BEFSR411. It has a small switch built in and will be fine for what you need.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><br>
