                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Hikaru you just gave a ton of reasons why a router <span style="font-style: italic">might</span> be as good as using a gateway for 2 computers but no reasons why the original poster should spend the initial investment (well over 100 bucks for the hardware you described) when he could be online with both computers in less time than it takes to read this entire thread.
<br />

<br />

<br />
<span style="color: blue">Bottom line:
<br />

<br />
Router = cost money but arguably easier to set up.
<br />

<br />
Gateway = Free, fast, at least as good as router for less than 4 computers. </span>
<br />

<br />

<br />
